text: Karyn Parsons (born October 8, 1966) is an American actress. She performs in television and movies. She was in Class Act in 1992. She also had the role of Hilary Banks in The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air. Parsons was born in Los Angeles. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Los Angeles
